  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nIn `eth2/state_processing/src/per_block_processing/verify_transfer.rs`\r\nVerifying the balance of `sender` should check against `amount + fee` rather just `amount`.\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nCurrently the code has a check `sender_balance >= transfer.amount`\r\n```rust\r\n    // Verify the sender has adequate balance.\r\n    verify!(\r\n        time_independent_only || sender_balance >= transfer.amount,\r\n        Invalid::FromBalanceInsufficient(transfer.amount, sender_balance)\r\n    );\r\n```\r\nWhich does not account for the fee.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\n`sender_balance >= total_amount`\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nChange `transfer.amount` to `total_amount` to also account for the fee.\r\n",
